==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|RNA}}
'''ribonucleic acid'''

# a [[derivative]] of [[DNA]] having [[ribose]] in place of [[deoxyribose]], and [[uracil]] in place of [[thymine]]; its primary [[function]] is in the [[transcription]] of [[genetic]] [[material]] and subsequent [[synthesis]] of [[protein]].

